list.item:
Are receiving Hepatitis C drug combination containing ombitasvir/paritaprevir/ritonavir, with or without dasabuvir, due to the potential for ALT elevations (see Warnings, 

                           RISK OF LIVER ENZYME ELEVATIONS WITH CONCOMITANT HEPATITIS C TREATMENT
                        ).

text.paragraph:
Concomitant Use with HCV Combination Therapy= Liver Enzyme Elevation: Do not co-administer MICROGESTIN and MICROGESTIN Fe with HCV drug combinations containing ombitasvir/paritaprevir/ritonavir, with or without dasabuvir, due to the potential for ALT elevations (see Warnings, 

   RISK OF LIVER ENZYME ELEVATIONS WITH CONCOMITANT HEPATITIS C TREATMENT
)
